ON HUB (beta) NOTE: The Research Collaboration Hub is intended for sharing research projects and research opportunities. The website is currently in beta mode. Instructions for filling out research projects Please indicate if this project is already completed, actively in progress, or has not yet been started. Also indicate in the email and phone number fields what is the appropriate contact information for the PI or research team. Under the research fields and research type headings, please choose the most appropriate category or categories that fit the project (if no none of the categories match the research type, please notify your department). For keywords, please use NIH MeSH terms . A project title and brief description are necessary to complete the entry. Finally, please indicate if there are roles for medical students, residents, fellows or other faculty on this project. Instructions for search For keywords, please use NIH MeSH terms Close Research Cancer Research Center for Outcomes Research Institutional Review Board James Scholar Program Craig Fellowship UICOMP Research Day About  Education  Research  Patient Care  Departments  News  Giving INFORMATION FOR: Prospective Students  Current Students  Faculty & Staff  Alumni & Friends  Patients RESOURCES: UIC Directory  Blackboard  Event Calendar  Emergency Information  Contact Us  Apply Now  Give  Contact Us Connect with us!      If you have questions, comments, or problems accessing this site, please E-mail the webmaster   Search for:    © Copyright 2020 University of Illinois College of Medicine   | Privacy Statement College of Medicine | Chicago | Peoria | Rockford | Urbana                                                                                                                                                  